        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 6 at 3:35PM CDT until July 6 at 4:00PM CDT by NWS St Louis MO</headline>
        <description>At 335 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Orchard Farms,
or near St. Charles, moving northeast at 25 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and small hail.

SOURCE...Broadcast media reported.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
St. Charles, Florissant, Hazelwood, West Alton, Portage Des Sioux
and Orchard Farms.
</description>
        <instruction>Seek shelter inside a well-built structure and stay away from
windows. This storm has produced damaging winds.

Report severe weather to your nearest law enforcement agency or the
National Weather Service office in St Louis MO.</instruction>
